node.text: Thank you so much, Luke @zocobodypro ! It was a pretty intensive workout but I loved it! Luckily I don’t have to do that everyday 😅😂. 1 more day in quarantine, then back on the court! I can’t wait! 🎾

node.text:
Excited to have with me on tour and on vacation my favorite BEE SUN SAFE sunscreen Hydra Fresh face & body milk SPF50 of @apivita @apivitagreece. It does not only protect my skin, but also the environment as it does not contain any harmful sun-filters for the marine ecosystem. As a member of the APIVITA family, I couldn’t be more proud that 1% of BEE SUN SAFE sunscreens sales worldwide go to non-profit organizations helping the environment and the bees.

#apivita #apivitagreece #beesunsafe #celanbeautycleanocean #onepercentfortheplanet
